snippet: Cornell’s Kyle Dake, a 21-year-old senior who is the top-ranked wrestler at 165 pounds, defeated No. 13 Zach Toal of Missouri and No. 3 Tyler Caldwell of Oklahoma State and was named the outstanding wrestler at Grapple at the Garden,
abstract: Kyle Dake of Cornell is named the outstanding wrestler at Grapple at the Garden, Madison Garden's first collegiate wrestling event, after defeating Zach Toal of Missouri and Tyler Caldwell of Oklahoma.

headline.main: Dake Shines at Garden Wrestling Event
